data.description: Offering expansive vistas of stunning Lake Livingston, this beautiful and recently renovated residence in sought after Forest Cove delivers on idyllic lakeside living.  Sited on an expansive corner lot, this two story home showcases three spacious bedrooms including dual Primary Bedrooms with dedicated en suites, as well as two additional bathrooms.  Open and bright floorpan and generous windows throughout the home feature expansive views and extensive natural light.  Thoughtful layout on sprawling lot with breathtaking views.  This stunning home features an open concept with the kitchen as the heart of the home.  Oversized windows throughout display the home’s scenic natural surroundings.  Enjoy breathtaking sunrises on your stunning wrap-around porch perfect for relaxing.  Embrace the outdoors in the sprawling front yard, offering a serene retreat.  Generous storage throughout home with includes many spacious closets.  Updates throughout.  Tranquility awaits- welcome home!
